        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God has shepherded me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All my life to this very day."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord is my Shepherd."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All my life I have lacked nothing."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He preserved me and arranged my daily walk."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He patiently works to transform my soul."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He brought me to the church, the one true flock"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Here we enjoy Him and His name extol."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though there were times in the valleys,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I did not fear for He was with me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He used every joy and distress"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To conform and to bless,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Looking back now I can confess…"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
