            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I onward run for I must finish my course,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As long as He grants me more days to live."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He supplies me with the grace to be my force."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s always near, full of more life to give."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is not much time remaining."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "While I have breath He’s sustaining."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As I follow Him and don’t stray,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then I know in that day"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By His mercy I will still say…"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
